Each health maintenance organization application or offer of enrollment shall contain or be accompanied by, and each form of health maintenance organization subscriber contract shall contain, a full and clear statement of:
The items specified in § 19-714 of this subtitle;
The rate of periodic payment;
When the coverage is effective and what restrictions, if any, apply to preexisting conditions;
All standards for cancellation of enrollment or denial of reenrollment; and
Service priorities, if any, in epidemic or other emergency or catastrophic conditions that may cause an unusually high demand for medical services.
